data.description: Welcome to your new move-in ready home with plenty of upgrades and an enormous backyard oasis! With NO HOA and plenty of  space, you can truly make it your own! Completed at the end of 2017, this home needs no work and is ready for its new owners! Upon  entering, you will notice the high ceilings and the open floor plan making for a grand entryway. With beautiful wood tile  floors throughout, crown moulding,  granite countertops, white shaker cabinets, and newer stainless appliances, this home has been  immaculately maintained. The open kitchen overlooks the main living room, formal dining room and backyard, with the most stunning  view of the garden! The HUGE backyard features a  screened in lanai with plenty of space and a beautiful custom-designed  garden complete with a walking path and bench seating for taking in the views or relaxing with your favorite book. Brand new raised  garden beds with built-in irrigation sit along the back fence. The enormous 18x32ft workshop features two garage doors on either  side for easy access to lawn equipment or parking for unloading. It also features a separate room that can be converted to an in-law suite! With all of these features, there is still plenty of space to install a pool! With no HOA, the possibilities are endless!  Located conveniently  near shopping, local schools and major highways, this home is a MUST SEE! Come check it out today!
